                                  <p>Once you get the desired CDR, it will provide you the gate pass to your dream destination. CDR (Competency Development Report) showcases your technical abilities which you have acquired through the engineering experiences, and EA is the assessing authority who tries to assess your skills and knowledge.</p>
                                  
                                  <p>The EA Migration Skills Assessment Booklet provides a complete picture of what is desired by the EA with all the guidelines laid down very carefully. On top of that, even if you do not understand the booklet, there are online services who provide CDR help and can review the requirements of CDR for you.</p>
                                  
                                  <p>When a Petroleum Engineer wishes to apply for a skilled migration visa to Australia, it is imperative for him to fulfill the competency indicators, as required by the EA. If you think that CDR is just a short report on your professional achievements, you must be mistaken. A CDR has three important sections to it.</p>
                                  
