                                  </ul>
                                   
                                  <h2>1: Continuing Professional Development</h2> 
                                  <p>This section requires the candidate to lay down entire details of the knowledge attained till date and build a graph of his or her educational achievements. It is in the format of a tabular representation of engagements/activities which shows your skills and achievements in the field of engineering. It also involves the mention of workshops for skill enhancement, and seminars participated in as well as details of a research project as part of an internship or college curriculum and journals subscribed to, etc. It is a section which tries to understand your enthusiasm for grasping the subject and your initiative to be updated continuously with the changing scenarios. It measures your growth in the area of specialization.</p> 
        
